data.description: Beautiful three bedroom ranch home on a large half acre lot!!  Hardwood flooring, open concept living all on one floor!  Both a living room and a cozy family room complete with a woodburning fire place.  Primary suite with an adjoining bathroom as well!  New roof, gutters and downspouts in 2019, new furnace 2015, new AC 2017, new sump pump, hot water heater and fencing!  Perfect summer entertainment in the fully fenced yard, complete with a patio and fire pit!  Don't miss out on fantastic home!! **Back on market due to buyers inability to secure financing**
